<h1> Dug</h1>
<p> "Dug" is a playlist that holds all of your saved tracks for easy access. 
    <br> It automatically keeps updated in the background so you don't have to think about it.
</p>
<h3>Dug will need a playlist to write into
</h3>


<h3>Choose an exsisting playlist to become dug:</h3>

<form id="dug_credentials" action="">
    <select id="dug_select" multiple size="<%=playlists.length%>">
        <% playlists.forEach(list => { %>
        <option value="<%=list.id%>"> <%=list.name%></option>
        <%});%>

    </select>
    <br>
</form>


<button class="btn btn-default" id="submit_dug">Submit</button>


<script src="/public/javascripts/enable_dug.js" type="text/javascript"></script>